text.tspan: Campana is Filum's younger brother. He is always so
positive and I think that's very refreshing. Filum kinda
finds how optomistic Campana is to be a bit "sickening"
sometimes, to quote him. Yep, older siblings can be
jerks sometimes, even if they truly love their younger
siblings, which I know Filum does. Campana is actually
two separate organisms, but they're both Campana. It
seems a bit weird, right? I think so. Anyway, the face is
one organism, and the body is another, and they can
separate. He does this to sneak around sometimes, but
I don't know why he sneaks around. Maybe he's getting
snacks. Whatever the reason, his eyes glow, so the
"sneaking around" part doesn't really work. It's funny,
though.
Campana
Filum but tiny and also bell
Age: 17
Species: Ghoul
Alignment: Good
"how can you see me?"
It's him !!!
